出去食就得唔驚影響人<br />\n當然你住村屋要住到入天水圍就緊係唔方便"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"見到人成個rack 擺出去做 <br />\n好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b713de104ca9e90afaeed071007e763314cb316","tid":2454051,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0e55c2d70a6705ac5dbf85dc04cc74ca72b6dc5","tid":2454051,"uid":374452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b095dcfaefe54aa32b1588c94d30221ca36a53c9","tid":2454051,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1dba2105348fa09fc0279f2f713eb6ebd6dc3afb","tid":2454051,"uid":374452,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"我係有丁權嗰位，我都覺得村屋丁屋真心好多不便（利申，我支持收曬d地黎起公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:16:16.000Z","msg":"竟然有啲咁嘅人"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"其實好多新一代既圍村人都支持收翻曬d地黎起公屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔支持起公屋<br />\n支持起居屋"},{"pid":"9c3bd8035d97a255c5281f368e712601e9e69acb","tid":2454051,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec141cdf6b5fc0135e46299b13eabad4cd8a9ebd","tid":2454051,"uid":25557,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bb9285b368b5dbe2cbd67c5e30decc4a1853563","tid":2454051,"uid":90946,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"好撚多昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交通普遍都唔方便<br />\n有部分村屋前後左右都貼住人地間屋衰撚過公屋<br />\n<br />\n好處地方大啲，小人過住市中心，車位平，露台普遍大過私樓，有錢嘅租/買連天台多個天台用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"住得入先多蟲<br />\n舉個例子，天水圍西鐵站隔離啲村屋<br />\n成條村都起曬屋已經冇蟲<br />\n行三分鐘就西鐵站，仲有圖書館泳池，<br />\n過條馬路就街市惠康<br />\n渣車轉個彎就直出大欖隧道<br />\n二千尺仲要有車位，你細心望下果啲屋仲有自己花園"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"果度真係做到無蚊蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgm