c3bd8035d97a255c5281f368e712601e9e69acb","tid":2454051,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec141cdf6b5fc0135e46299b13eabad4cd8a9ebd","tid":2454051,"uid":25557,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bb9285b368b5dbe2cbd67c5e30decc4a1853563","tid":2454051,"uid":90946,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"好撚多昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交通普遍都唔方便<br />\n有部分村屋前後左右都貼住人地間屋衰撚過公屋<br />\n<br />\n好處地方大啲，小人過住市中心，車位平，露台普遍大過私樓，有錢嘅租/買連天台多個天台用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"住得入先多蟲<br />\n舉個例子，天水圍西鐵站隔離啲村屋<br />\n成條村都起曬屋已經冇蟲<br />\n行三分鐘就西鐵站，仲有圖書館泳池，<br />\n過條馬路就街市惠康<br />\n渣車轉個彎就直出大欖隧道<br />\n二千尺仲要有車位，你細心望下果啲屋仲有自己花園"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"果度真係做到無蚊蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？條村有請滅蟲公司？<br />\n不過住果度小左住村屋環境靜嘅feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然好多人都鐘意住方便嘅村屋<br />\n二千呎有花園車位好多都係乜乜花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行過多小小坑頭村逼埋一堆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a5PN10F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa5PN10F.png&h=dd1006fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"勁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c2f01eca0e259f6c78d2e76549dbee9b8474ef","tid":2454051,"uid":60642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b6fe8d8e8753f9a0edffac7ec4c6125e7a04ec1","tid":2454051,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"如果想買丁屋，做到八成按<br />\n有咩地方注意？<br />\n成日聽到話做唔足按揭，又有好多地契問題（例如可能霸左官地），又多圍村佬哈哈霸霸，又要比化糞池等等<br />\n有冇巴打可以比d買村屋心得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"要睇清楚自己有冇路權，最好搵啲專買賣村屋嘅律師，如果擔心自己霸左官地，可以搵啲公司過嚟做測量，最好買啲新起嘅村屋，應該會少好多圍頭佬，化糞池我就兩年先吸一次，如果多人住就唔知了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有最後一點就係千祈咪撚買元朗嘅村屋"},{"pid":"ae674023db5d53aab81feaaac7d962160c7e72da","tid":2454051,"uid":60642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d0ab293ac9194da2960614ae9a93de0036fd5ee","tid":2454051,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311a6361f38515d7874ac7ec5e47a5e0172d5e5b","tid":2454051,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d73dd78db79a1e0656a6d86e812f0dc45941d85e","tid":2454051,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:34:47.000Z","msg":"加埋天台地下花園唔止2100"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"至少1300萬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"2015年大埔買差唔多，近路邊。依家千三萬，九曲十三彎入村或者有"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"我住緊依邊要2千萬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾年前屋企人用千四萬買"},{"pid":"c97b68c0bbe931c3575a793d98e88ea109206ef6","tid":2454051,"uid":60642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f8b747332ee22fb26f7a7ed2dc2236ef11decb6","tid":2454051,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ab9c6d3863060967006b7f50f8e9378406a950","tid":2454051,"uid":226829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"上網係咪仲係焗挨 $298 3Mb/8Mb老電ADSL？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"唔係，我用緊香港寬頻1000M"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"自從六七年前有間公司，專幫村屋鋪光纖，依家好多好多村屋已經有光纖上網"},{"pid":"bf1a0b5cbb6cfee26c69caec6bb23bc7908608a4","tid":2454051,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae674023db5d53aab81feaaac7d962160c7e72da","tid":2454051,"uid":60642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d0ab293ac9194da2960614ae9a93de0036fd5ee","tid":