haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"係 一年比住私樓慳好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（車位唔駛錢 3架26 1架46） <br />\n又無管理處要交<br />\n行出市區十零分鐘 抵住過大西北好多私樓（尚悅 溱泊 個啲）<br />\n空氣又唔差 好過住市區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夜晚又寧靜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"元朗近市村屋仲有大把地嘅得返唔係好多<br />\n你返屋企洗唔洗過天橋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a96ed1eb4da248797b5d01c4d70e2dcdde9841e","tid":2454051,"uid":161806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd72b8eeb83b05f223d097861fb9f120dd935c8","tid":2454051,"uid":66275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56227d6e83fe9ba25e4bdb2830836dcac409255d","tid":2454051,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b79317c9bb2d8871252c930b4b01c87ad53310c","tid":2454051,"uid":66275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"我呢排睇緊錦上路 大棠嘅村屋，但好少好啲嘅盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"如果你搭巴士出入<br />\n錦上路shell油站果度一帶都幾好嘅<br />\n較啱時間出門口，五分鐘車到大欖隧道<br />\n錦上路站隔離應該幾貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"姐係蓮花地個邊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:01:44.000Z","msg":"應該係石湖塘 水流田 水盞田嗰啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ae27e0c71299739ef157d84f99a2a691c3d898","tid":2454051,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3e32633ee60f7a54ba263ff35a9b105bc9fd56e","tid":2454051,"uid":374452,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"605cb694a1fb7f5d52ada11238932dd2b1a315b3","tid":2454051,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0e55c2d70a6705ac5dbf85dc04cc74ca72b6dc5","tid":2454051,"uid":374452,"like":0,"disli